data.description: Beautiful 3 bed, 2.5 bath in Mirror Lake Golf Community. The hard wood floors have just been refinished as well as the upstairs bathroom. Private drive to the 2 car garage located under the home. Fenced backyard on one side and a large backpack. The oversized master is on the main level. The house has a full basement.
